  "wikitext": "\nA device, system or service, external to vessels, designed and operated to enhance safe and efficient navigation of individual vessels and/or vessel traffic.\n\n\nOther forms: Aids to Navigation (plural), AtoN\n\n\n''This definition of the term Aid to Navigation is in accordance with the IALA Constitution.<br>The use of the definition from the original IALA Dictionary has been discontinued.''\n\n\n{{languages|Aid to Navigation}}\n[[Category:1.1 Basic Terms]]\n[[Category:Alphabetical Index]]\n[[Category:IALA Dictionary 2016 Revision]]\n[[Category:IALA Dictionary 2023 Revision]]\n[[Category:Approved by DWG]]"
